exports[`shipped agents render cleanly > resolves model tiers on both targets and snapshots output > research-agent-claude 1`] = `
"---
name: research-agent
description: "Multi-step investigation role that produces a synthesized issue brief from policy, codebase, and external sources. Use when a controller needs context for design brainstorming and the workflow has decided research is warranted. Do not use for implementation, code review, or single-source lookups."
tools: Read, Grep, Bash, WebFetch, WebSearch, Agent
---

Investigate the issue across policy, codebase, and external precedent.
Coordinate parallel sub-investigations when the workflow expects it; otherwise
do the work directly with read-only tools.
Synthesize findings into a single brief — do not dump raw output.
Return the brief in the format the dispatching skill specifies.
"
`;

